# Managed by Puppet

Host *
ForwardAgent <%= @forward_agent %>
HostbasedAuthentication <%= @hostbased_authentication %>
EnableSSHKeySign <%= @enable_ssh_key_sign %>
ForwardX11 no
RhostsRSAAuthentication no
RSAAuthentication yes
PasswordAuthentication <%= @password_authentication %>
GSSAPIAuthentication no
GSSAPIDelegateCredentials no
BatchMode no
CheckHostIP yes
AddressFamily any
StrictHostKeyChecking ask
Port 22
Protocol 2
Ciphers chacha20-poly1305@openssh.com,aes256-gcm@openssh.com,aes128-gcm@openssh.com,aes256-ctr,aes192-ctr,aes128-ctr
KexAlgorithms curve25519-sha256@libssh.org,diffie-hellman-group-exchange-sha256
MACs hmac-sha2-512-etm@openssh.com,hmac-sha2-256-etm@openssh.com,hmac-ripemd160-etm@openssh.com,umac-128-etm@openssh.com,hmac-sha2-512,hmac-sha2-256,hmac-ripemd160
Tunnel no
PermitLocalCommand no
UseRoaming no

SendEnv LANG LC_*
HashKnownHosts yes

<%- if @known_host_sssd -%>
GlobalKnownHostsFile /var/lib/sss/pubconf/known_hosts
ProxyCommand /usr/bin/sss_ssh_knownhostsproxy -p %p %h
<%- end -%>
PubkeyAuthentication <%= @pubkey_authentication %>
